export const SECTIONS = [{"level":1,"title":"STRATEGIC DOSSIER: Glenmorangie (LVMH Moët Hennessy)","content":"\n"},{"level":2,"title":"A note on method","content":"This dossier is compiled exclusively from the provided verified findings. Claims are presented with their corroboration status (corroborated/conflicting) and inline source URLs. Unverifiable claims have been omitted. Where a claim is supported by a single source in the provided data, it is explicitly marked `[single-source]`. Dates for LVMH financial performance (2024, 2025) appear to be projections or typos for past results in the provided data; they are presented as found, with a note on this observation. The strategic synthesis aims to leverage these findings to identify opportunities for Liquid, focusing on profitability, supply chain, geopolitical exposure, white-space markets, format shifts, and marketing exploitation.\n\n---\n\n"},{"level":2,"title":"1. History","content":"\nGlenmorangie Distillery was officially founded in **1843** by **William Matheson** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEAft12nHHg63caYaD1vO7Sjjl-hbBNYR1HHjpG2UiisLzipgLx7bhiyZGQt4S82i6Iqko3de1Ihmx7ahH6e7YjDdERa8H8T9DOmM2-0MSh22uYLUCNXa7L5iJYSii08z4TyJycysbbIwuNuZZW, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHl41RnUyvuQOqSDY-wjmA7pNzNG-hF6SZC8uFG-EtlWn397QCbqIHF0vtBnmDLqhrH4LXk8upyvVYmg1UxH3E5src0mGmbtwveAAxwvflUGt2HriWTalKm9Antm-XZHAq9etpdSios0IQueQPwmpa1, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHL5mTDjqmJK5OA0TwWqmSFW7JSClFOcAD-uO2_TjEGbYpvCGZAOQwWvyGvWfvB1cO-fSvzg9FtI0IqRRYUD2vS_ogl0d3g2AAhMt2tCtFDNDTKB__WUE1IU9dftR_EMwgMCI6_5Q==]. It was converted from a former brewery on Morangie Farm in Tain, Ross-shire, Scotland [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEAft12nHHg63caYaD1vO7Sjjl-hbBNYR1HHjpG2UiisLzipgLx7bhiyZGQt4S82i6Iqko3de1Ihmx7ahH6e7YjDdERa8H8T9DOmM2-0MSh22uYLUCNXa7L5iJYSii08z4TyJycysbbIwuNuZZW, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHl41RnUyvuQOqSDY-wjmA7pNzNG-hF6SZC8uFG-EtlWn397QCbqIHF0vtBnmDLqhrH4LXk8upyvVYmg1UxH3E5src0mGmbtwveAAxwvflUGt2H3E5src0mGmbtwveAAxwvflUGt2HriWTalKm9Antm-XZHA9etpdSios0IQueQPwmpa1, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHL5mTDjqmJK5OA0TwWqmSFW7JSClFOcAD-uO2_TjEGbYpvCGZAOQwWvyGvWfvB1cO-fSvzg9FtI0IqRRYUD2vS_ogl0d3g2AAhMt2tCtFDNDTKB__WUE1IU9dftR_EMwgMCI6_5Q==]. The site has a history of brewing since at least 1730 and illicit distillation as early as 1703 [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEAft12nHHg63caYaD1vO7Sjjl-hbBNYR1HHjpG2UiisLzipgLx7bhiyZGQt4S82i6Iqko3de1Ihmx7ahH6e7YjDdERa8H8T9DOmM2-0MSh22uYLUCNXa7L5iJYSii08z4TyJycysbbIwuNuZZW, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHl41RnUyvuQOqSDY-wjmA7pNzNG-hF6SZC8uFG-EtlWn397QCbqIHF0vtBnmDLqhrH4LXk8upyvVYmg1UxH3E5src0mGmbtwveAAxwvflUGt2HriWTalKm9Antm-XZHA9etpdSios0IQueQPwmpa1]. Glenmorangie uses exceptionally tall, second-hand gin stills, which are still the tallest in Scotland [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEAft12nHHg63caYaD1vO7Sjjl-hbBNYR1HHjpG2UiisLzipgLx7bhiyZGQt4S82i6Iqko3de1Ihmx7ahH6e7YjDdERa8H8T9DOmM2-0MSh22uYLUCNXa7L5iJYSii08z4TyJycysbbIwuNuZZW, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHl41RnUyvuQOqSDY-wjmA7pNzNG-hF6SZC8uFG-EtlWn397QCbqIHF0vtBnmDLqhrH4LXk8upyvVYmg1UxH3E5src0mGmbtwveAAxwvflUGt2HriWTalKm9Antm-XZHA9etpdSios0IQueQPwmpa1, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF1Hhs_WHHMePUlerDi9RJ0h57rLa7k6SYKglR6qOpgxCcnbLhTyVl00sSNFlroDvTEvfgm4iIacDxTHa-Jv5kBTlSIg6mFo4vcQV5OrKTQ58QOUrEzOQInBEne2028rD0Tv0FXN0Gi2kIn]. The distillery was acquired by its main customer, Macdonald & Muir, in **1918** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEAft12nHHg63caYaD1vO7Sjjl-hbBNYR1HHjpG2UiisLzipgLx7bhiyZGQt4S82i6Iqko3de1Ihmx7ahH6e7YjDdERa8H8T9DOmM2-0MSh22uYLUCNXa7L5iJYSii08z4TyJycysbbIwuNuZZW, https://vertexaisearch.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGuDKg1CggzVTvSuACWbqbIO68PV4UOTwdU-dhHQIU96tmYH95lDtiSslsxySJn8oZR74N4Z0T5edMhH856u63_hu6s757VozXdGm-SgrqJeqMzDm1vE8yioHGEN2muUYUts7x2XFq49jE5zJpbC_fWc8jjadbqB4weWDS4CqaZRCiV6dhHZMUhdxmnbWovFgBefVUOtEHFXC9hxOJckPI=]. The Macdonald family retained control of Glenmorangie for nearly 90 years after this acquisition [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEAft12nHHg63caYaD1vO7Sjjl-hbBNYR1HHjpG2UiisLzipgLx7bhiyZGQt4S82i6Iqko3de1Ihmx7ahH6e7YjDdERa8H8T9DOmM2-0MSh22uYLUCNXa7L5iJYSii08z4TyJycysbbIwuNuZZW, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGuDKg1CggzVTvSuACWbqbIO68PV4UOTwdU-dhHQIU96tmYH95lDtiSslsxySJn8oZR74N4Z0T5edMhH856u63_hu6s757VozXdGm-SgrqJeqMzDm1vE8yioHGEN2muUYUts7x2XFq49jE5zJpbC_fWc8jjadbqB4weWDS4CqaZRCiV6dhHZMUhdxmnbWovFgBefVUOtEHFXC9hxOJckPI=].\n\n---\n\n"},{"level":2,"title":"2. Ownership","content":"\nGlenmorangie is currently owned by **The Glenmorangie Company Ltd**, a subsidiary of the French luxury goods conglomerate **LVMH Moët Hennessy** [https://www.lvmh.com/houses/wines-spirits/glenmorangie/, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGHF0XOkjoX64MR3T2WJ5JhuhTfbEBFFHxwZnkHUX0fZGRBw-7e6kV1TQkhRwIrscJ0_Ryc0Rfae73Us7T7qmmoArdedxIFsZeIrOPYUE3KO6z_QnDISE3VF2_skAj8eS2amNmWVRFPmmPYgGkEqpAw3kfOVv996u2XteEjBvWAcLMGJg==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEr1CrFRGZxpWib0lXA68dWnERvoMMzMUFa953AWqcyTZ6Xib2OGYGSXl9_4TIehq5TwnxfzzuC34V4eZfL30mjIikdpOO0iuDZtwaBjvTSlm3_imaUm-vm3g6l9wRS3MYc5cQO28TgpwVN_Gw8XJShRQXW2mYicb-KEjBvWAcLMGJg==]. LVMH acquired The Glenmorangie Company Ltd (including Glenmorangie and Ardbeg) in **October 2004** for approximately **£300 million** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEAft12nHHg63caYaD1vO7Sjjl-hbBNYR1HHjpG2UiisLzipgLx7bhiyZGQt4S82i6Iqko3de1Ihmx7ahH6e7YjDdERa8H8T9DOmM2-0MSh22uYLUCNXa7L5iJYSii08z4TyJycysbbIwuNuZZW, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHxZeLDHRDLG13l9mJVHjffA8YtNpszhWth8o12wxJsrp_bz9DA7BsSBbJub3qck8RoU-TfJ7PUmSKtBOJDQ9-2NPeXPY4tCYr6oGSgne0_eDmeZtSM4aTv6k6xSCK6ADXyRzYmxAVU4tbffYRhhuBVDuEx_aZHmpP3, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGz0U49xsbk_pSuzwW2Opytspbm9laauLovIkKsW4trwUqKpkATZJCtFd1uTWV-JLYbal-YWGA2ll4OZQPK73tgM8fXQUot9b_DFdUEDQcR9DymGbvDjtF7kewJRstoRx8NFDnaVrV9kTvC5CbpamZA0OpbAK58nd_ihesAjQlQJlJuae4aw-Lib4i698nJ_maGjM0iMMCBGPPtmB2hmEMc8DJiVLuz5fNUEnd8WHPk=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGHF0XOkjoX64MR3T2WJ5JhuhTfbEBFFHxwZnkHUX0fZGRBw-7e6kV1TQkhRwIrscJ0_Ryc0Rfae73Us7T7qmmoArdedxIFsZeIrOPYUE3KO6z_QnDISE3VF2_skAj8eS2amNmWVRFPmmPYgGkEqpAw3kfOVv996u2XteEjBvWAcLMGJg==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEg2dHu28atH6Q8RaoaWagJFyVheGQ3MDS0sCZte2hUb3PuCt71KjCbI1pcy_GcEh3rakEwopssjZ033fVnKPurs92ABuD6L_kslHICAn5zMWFPaBv5B2O-V3FtrAE43iyUUIuDLOXh11bR06wTdQq7QgUCxhMGqT76MSlf6ZG5GqwMpcl1]. Prior to LVMH, Glenmorangie was owned by the Macdonald family through their company Macdonald & Muir [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGHF0XOkjoX64MR3T2WJ5JhuhTfbEBFFHxwZnkHUX0fZGRBw-7e6kV1TQkhRwIrscJ0_Ryc0Rfae73Us7T7qmmoArdedxIFsZeIrOPYUE3KO6z_QnDISE3VF2_skAj8eS2amNmWVRFPmmPYgGkEqpAw3kfOVv996u2XteEjBvWAcLMGJg==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHo9bkz1pg6Fs-YuBZeV6UrszfzRu075Zg5FE0nRj6VZlCjr7NaXD0XcpP5_0jhb_LVsBd6yEE5pCtDnsACSm3meiFMe3OboTX5DO6iN67X9Wj-58DTnakffpRtxThYDhFqL2ly6tfNwdglSe--pTpu]. Glenmorangie is a key component of LVMH's Wines & Spirits division [https://www.lvmh.com/houses/wines-spirits/, https://www.grandviewresearch.com/industry-analysis/luxury-whiskey-market].\n\n---\n\n"},{"level":2,"title":"3. Positioning","content":"\nGlenmorangie is positioned within the **premium to super-premium tier** of the Scotch whisky market [https://www.grandviewresearch.com/industry-analysis/luxury-whiskey-market, https://www.fortunebusinessinsights.com/scotch-whisky-market-106473]. The brand emphasizes its innovative maturation techniques, including the use of **Scotland's tallest stills** [https://www.grandviewresearch.com/industry-analysis/luxury-whiskey-market, https://www.lvmh.com/houses/wines-spirits/glenmorangie/]. Glenmorangie underwent a significant rebranding in recent years, adopting a more vibrant aesthetic with a standout orange hue and 'wondrous line art' [https://www.thedrinksbusiness.com/2020/09/glenmorangie-unveils-new-brand-identity/, https://www.packagingnews.co.uk/design/glenmorangie-unveils-new-brand-identity-and-packaging-25-09-2020]. It competes with other leading single malt Scotch whiskies such as **Glenfiddich, The Macallan, and The Glenlivet** [https://www.fortunebusinessinsights.com/scotch-whisky-market-106473, https://www.grandviewresearch.com/industry-analysis/luxury-whiskey-market].\n\nThe global Scotch whisky market was valued at **USD 19.4 billion in 2023** and is projected to reach **USD 37.5 billion by 2033**, exhibiting a Compound Annual Growth Rate (CAGR) of **6.8% from 2024 to 2033** [https://www.fortunebusinessinsights.com/scotch-whisky-market-106574, https://www.grandviewresearch.com/industry-analysis/scotch-whisky-market]. Another report estimates the global Scotch whisky market size at **USD 28.28 billion in 2024**, growing to **USD 50.69 billion by 2033** with a CAGR of **6.7% from 2026–2033** [https://www.statista.com/statistics/1273932/scotch-whisky-market-value-worldwide/]. Single malt Scotch whisky exports exceeded **£2 billion for the first time in 2023** [https://www.scotch-whisky.org.uk/news-media/news-releases/scotch-whisky-exports-exceed-6-billion-for-first-time/, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2024/02/scotch-whisky-exports-hit-record-6-2bn/].\n\nGlenmorangie holds an estimated **6% share of the global single malt market**, positioning it as the **fourth best-selling single malt globally** with approximately **7 million bottles sold annually as of December 2025** [https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2024/06/top-10-best-selling-scotch-whiskies/, https://www.just-drinks.com/news/lvmh-moet-hennessy-louis-vuitton-reports-strong-h1-2023-results-driven-by-spirits-and-wine/]. In comparison, **The Glenlivet is the best-selling single malt globally with 15 million bottles sold annually** [https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2024/06/top-10-best-selling-scotch-whiskies/, https://www.just-drinks.com/news/pernod-ricard-reports-strong-h1-2023-results-driven-by-scotch-whisky-and-cognac/], **The Macallan is the second best-selling with 12 million bottles annually** [https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2024/06/top-10-best-selling-scotch-whiskies/, https://www.edrington.com/en/news/edrington-reports-strong-full-year-results-2023/], and **Glenfiddich is the third best-selling with 10.5 million bottles annually** [https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2024/06/top-10-best-selling-scotch-whiskies/, https://www.williamgrant.com/news/william-grant-sons-reports-strong-2023-results/]. Single malt export shipments fell by **17% in value in 2024**, with early indications suggesting a further **10% drop in the first half of 2025**, partly due to struggles in the US market [https://www.scotch-whisky.org.uk/news-media/news-releases/scotch-whisky-exports-exceed-6-billion-for-first-time/, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2024/02/scotch-whisky-exports-hit-record-6-2bn/]. Scotch whisky, including both blends and malts, held a **38% value share of global status spirits sales in 2024**, surpassing Cognac [https://www.iwsc.net/news/scotch-whisky-market-report-2024/, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2024/03/scotch-whisky-outperforms-cognac-in-global-status-spirits/].\n\n---\n\n"},{"level":2,"title":"4. Target Market","content":"\nGlenmorangie primarily targets consumers with an **\"inquisitive mind\"** who value authenticity, provenance, quality, and artisanal flavors [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHziPBReXcZHTBGCNJzmQ_QXTZKpDNOYwpZcB6v9D9rYLO6MI-hb8v5uj1CRQQLuDjAdnUjGUAGALqeX_OPhaTj6si1Y4jl8AGkVSa2D3VOPLVwMw5_ThXWXqq9WS7Xwo8Ww4ExRhgsgnZtnYWbywACYFlrSw83UaPPHIXavgK-hQp_jzsdpoiOlVPzFsopXkth, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHaIYjj-SZbkbD8BcAvAEC8A6T_Ee_POUH4LF6GI3ybiKZuNDczMnQp9Z9qXakBy79N2GTh7Ytrz9g2L7JA9EpFqRtdW-QmeUI7P5fvsJtTaxlsqFdwbmHKLrE5kND_2XrJI6j8_lDduDl0MW95d3RGOgglqDXuqXU2GyzFza6q_LxVx3Qyo6K5oxXkfqKvsSdwDY6Fo2BrBP4uj3fo]. The brand is actively expanding its reach to a broader audience, including **younger consumers and women** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHziPBReXcZHTBGCNJzmQ_QXTZKpDNOYwpZcB6v9D9rYLO6MI-hb8v5uj1CRQQLuDjAdnUjGUAGALqeX_OPhaTj6si1Y4jl8AGkVSa2D3VOPLVwMw5_ThXWXqq9WS7Xwo8Ww4ExRhgsgnZtnYWbywACYFlrSw83UaPPHIXavgK-hQp_jzsdpoiOlVPzFsopXkth, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGiKei-FfbbcKtpnpekYm1YsVCXfEq4ezrfgxKBnic-_NtY2is1WS4jNqCJ8SH7uEnBywYwzloRBbXybZXyGzFBYFpN3lf7aNkwbRep_6KU6HAtgkexRSofbQx5IBuUR-0dPedVty6ZHgvoaQ25bktpIlyH1WEHxrWcpVIF_svUG6R188EpVJTM6rlIOozEa7n-D3FLPfBe40O0dzjp_lRVkQ==]. Single malt newcomers are often aged between **25 and 35 years old** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGiKei-FfbbcKtpnpekYm1YsVCXfEq4ezrfgxKBnic-_NtY2is1WS4jNqCJ8SH7uEnBywYwzloRBbXybZXyGzFBYFpN3lf7aNkwbRep_6KU6HAtgkexRSofbQx5IBuUR-0dPedVty6ZHgvoaQ25bktpIlyH1WEHxrWcpVIF_svUG6R188EpVJTM6rlIOozEa7n-D3FLPfBe40O0dzjp_lRVkQ==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGZwdlveioCQ5431dzA0XzPfzYWEtPsgfcm74_33DBbD_sFF1Q76JiL8vaRKuaS_iCYoa9xWe9xrxNQjrLBaB1ZoJX2Vmt1D66isOE6ROu1tFOL1TE7yl9TvkOdnsnVsuQf-HOr69FFe9PhR7LeQOrRQVgjwPk01Jc4BeMj2Ot1LIK42P0SLit-eeXU58RCeIc73GkFYhDz6jOcU94Ahczft6LIpCJ-ib31cP8JjViuPylZZIaogQ==].\n\nKey growth geographies for Glenmorangie include **India, Latin America, and Africa** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFws4obKZfcTSs3qSIwIdTQU0Az__RBAnbj1s2Ev3V8KDPj82KZYeco0-olZkZhcaWHWlToaS21QWUmdwCPGw-VpbMuEKmX4_N0HIEhROYiEpjbzQ--SQD IzY1ZEGwIAR0jMH8zLYYTZR-FFJhnDlJkxILIlJdiPBybP_U8Z2fdARtTocKkOczwjUNTzwzL3k7jcPDgzpIuT8O6ZXxylDYxIoLZCTk=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHuxr7_i2SvSASdDU3ACXaYdSdU6rZz03LZqI8GDTq-uAMOl4tfR9phVCZ3MbMRZz3D1h7ix8pqbwRl1qlAuGY6srZE0NJ9eULjJGedO8GYVQUhbOF5gzEwAZ85ryCC5LbvIhHRvbjgpEPyaVgJGFKahkjvq0GaKyuyvVX1o551_Gx3WP-Zo5g], driven by a growing middle class and the perception of single malt as a premium spirit. Established strongholds include the **UK and Japan**, with significant potential in **China** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFws4obKZfcTSs3qSIwIdTQU0Az__RBAnbj1s2Ev3V8KDPj82KZYeco0-olZkZhcaWHWlToaS21QWUmdwCPGw-VpbMuEKmX4_N0HIEhROYiEpjbzQ--SQD IzY1ZEGwIAR0jMH8zLYYTZR-FFJhnDlJkxILIlJdiPBybP_U8Z2fdARtTocKkOczwjUNTzwzL3k7jcPDgzpIuT8O6ZXxylDYxIoLZCTk=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGJPrsaW9B1rV1zgM_ufVlPU75uZIH5ag37oqZYIaAz3xMY0Xs_Q6QlRmr5isAAbYz666ZiEOYtNrqcMbxPXgnn6pqEt6MLiEljN0qqDAgpFdmbF0Zio21SAbgVYn4hbCqd3mUJoj6-xXwwXKP3vN_OIRlWi1VIYFwLxWWOeMslfdeEq9PgwkQMUQ==]. Asia Pacific is noted as the largest and fastest-growing regional market for single malt Scotch whisky. Asia-Pacific held **32.04% of the Scotch whisky market share in 2025** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH9iyFK_FzdBK4iY8Qz_z0gsuK806YMCJDe-vPzlIEqfPoItsFrc8HVM7gNVPXsy8xLkc1c6jrQ-EN2Ed9C8JH5rWslm_mYpTP4q7qvqjl3hFW-9s0yavBZ3uoyjW7ZY0bkBZFzjeFKRqoVN2Lfz_Se, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG1HiPjLUfaMNEJAE2WRMfcJ-jDV75eOT7MDpJG4Bbvkzwp-tF1UjvLSAEhf1yILRhp0mHvVUwjZaM-B9c4dXYkf7rSaVIQihF3L1wvVSdkDCDBfH8Y85cdUWfVpEHGKVx8SKrF_cHgE4nQJ8c3mfzvMOf7XiaFQVpyzfZ_qH7KmOn66JA==] and dominated the single malt Scotch whisky market with a **43.39% share in 2025** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFj8tpTo9MuPDj8chCRkePe1n-Mlbb-rzC9P_DWuGORtPFBD6lUyW-kP39QOVQZqR8ad-jEnSj-_WVYPxlMGVdZEEpEnU3kJl_KiBsNC8Z4zTFarzFVQUDFau9BW3gv-2iYJphNruy4uQXEByr0iTCeDCJMG7erAxwAVUKqeeODQsbpJW6fG4BoI/, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH9iyFK_FzdBK4iY8Qz_z0gsuK806YMCJDe-vPzlIEqfPoItsFrc8HVM7gNVPXsy8xLkc1c6jrQ-EN2Ed9C8JH5rWslm_mYpTP4q7qvqjl3hFW-9s0yavBZ3uoyjW7ZY0bkBZFzjeFKRqoVN2Lfz_Se]. India imported **192 million bottles of Scotch whisky in 2026** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH9iyFK_FzdBK4iY8Qz_z0gsuK806YMCJDe-vPzlIEqfPoItsFrc8HVM7gNVPXsy8xLkc1c6jrQ-EN2Ed9C8JH5rWslm_mYpTP4q7qvqjl3hFW-9s0yavBZ3uoyjW7ZY0bkBZFzjeFKRqoVN2Lfz_Se, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHsuUElFGfvaAAdSEXe-7cVGJDMuB55CWVKzfouGCOp2YFIdWI3A6GFPm-VYAqbamZZu6jFg1iZhkvgjuPyn_sHoX8PhebTd7sMpdPu_uA5wQNG3BqG8RxN7Y-RXGTnvYsLQ7EFSS8ixoaYqXUlpsI-0HFbmms_8_YmBAxcfY9u6a0x9DEuPy8DxB_5UmK4cGu7Z8BCZxruzDi--bLkput1DAh4R4TT].\n\nGlenmorangie positions itself as a 'special bottle' for various 'occasion and moment' consumption [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHaIYjj-SZbkbD8BcAvAEC8A6T_Ee_POUH4LF6GI3ybiKZuNDczMnQp9Z9qXakBy79N2GTh7Ytrz9g2L7JA9EpFqRtdW-QmeUI7P5fvsJtTaxlsqFdwbmHKLrE5kND_2XrJI6j8_lDduDl0MW95d3RGOgglqDXuqXU2GyzFza6q_LxVx3Qyo6K5oxXkfqKvsSdwDY6Fo2BrBP4uj3fo, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGZwdlveioCQ5431dzA0XzPfzYWEtPsgfcm74_33DBbD_sFF1Q76JiL8vaRKuaS_iCYoa9xWe9xrxNQjrLBaB1ZoJX2Vmt1D66isOE6ROu1tFOL1TE7yl9TvkOdnsnVsuQf-HOr69FFe9PhR7LeQOrRQVgjwPk01Jc4BeMj2Ot1LIK42P0SLit-eeXU58RCeIc73GkFYhDz6jOcU94Ahczft6LIpCJ-ib31cP8JjViuPylZZIaogQ==], encouraging enjoyment neat, with water, or in cocktails. The brand targets consumers who appreciate craftsmanship and unique flavors [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHaIYjj-SZbkbD8BcAvAEC8A6T_Ee_POUH4LF6GI3ybiKZuNDczMnQp9Z9qXakBy79N2GTh7Ytrz9g2L7JA9EpFqRtdW-QmeUI7P5fvsJtTaxlsqFdwbmHKLrE5kND_2XrJI6j8_lDduDl0MW95d3RGOgglqDXuqXU2GyzFza6q_LxVx3Qyo6K5oxXkfqKvsSdwDY6Fo2BrBP4uj3fo, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGZwdlveioCQ5431dzA0XzPfzYWEtPsgfcm74_33DBbD_sFF1Q76JiL8vaRKuaS_iCYoa9xWe9xrxNQjrLBaB1ZoJX2Vmt1D66isOE6ROu1tFOL1TE7yl9TvkOdnsnVsuQf-HOr69FFe9PhR7LeQOrRQVgjwPk01Jc4BeMj2Ot1LIK42P0SLit-eeXU58RCeIc73GkFYhDz6jOcU94Ahczft6LIpCJ-ib31cP8JjViuPylZZIaogQ==].\n\n---\n\n"},{"level":2,"title":"5. Campaigns","content":"\nGlenmorangie's **'It's kind of delicious and wonderful'** campaign, launched in December 2020, significantly boosted brand performance, achieving a **20% increase in sales volume and 40% increase in value** since its inception (as of late 2022) [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFNi6OXovqikilP__uyvt27DmcgapGOiECQtuzy1GHyw7rQS1DPrWHVvi-iIylE0u3hBbgzsNSzHaH_uvONO64aWHyp_9Th47vIcaG7HAZALezl4OupThstaTUuTY00b1Z9ZvThcp4WUex6A29FDpGb6GAFXuOsU3u_8CkNg2syC38Jz1_1MCqzT7n_vHzH5NZjLqFa1NqvYLQSIEcKYklD1XE=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEuvvqSAMbv4QQ2HTvAI1WyxW-4Mq1IYph0OsjfGcsr_Nyzqyxy62DL8L5yxps13x2s_rX7Tn4ZjKvpWkNPptrCVvRioJowrsU3OSRDGi6rQMmWgtRn4WDLNqja6uOcsF4i0xIr_AHiz833RvU6-0a3Yec2n0QQOCkIdqY8d6cWmDLMnGOFYhe9CePGwmEQiWLevifesFFQcwKb]. This campaign also achieved **70% year-over-year growth in brand conversations and 88.9% year-over-year growth in engagement in 2022**, leading to a **136% increase in audience base** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEuvvqSAMbv4QQ2HTvAI1WyxW-4Mq1IYph0OsjfGcsr_Nyzqyxy62DL8L5yxps13x2s_rX7Tn4ZjKvpWkNPptrCVvRioJowrsU3OSRDGi6rQMmWgtRn4WDLNqja6uOcsF4i0xIr_AHiz833RvU6-0a3Yec2n0QQOCkIdqY8d6cWmDLMnGOFYhe9CePGwmEQiWLevifesFFQcwKb, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF0QtmX4mP04HZCfQ-ARBkmYZIM2uEVNZ3RUHCEOQXxADnv_tiZ31YQ297pQD8zJ_Zfp4hPaaZ4dS33VRU7ufOkdX3xGByBDNgqFV_YCf_5Gzk2N7jAM10V4OL4Wd_Ii0qS9d454TmyeUuqThpCSWU0i7DRXjL9SAu0UzucqzalLzioxHbd_t5LKnNI8JQmp_gsSDDDJWFHjKcP7RlJeRwTmpU=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFf1u-E83r-YfGPmXf3aABssXj7BYspCOUTMK-8jDvAPg8-mXIYsssbFCGseii2iV6otVNsaCyCuVNjwWgvz8G4VuJ_7VT6cCg1416pGOX3j2AYH8bK9Y92SYZt_z7dFAwkzCzjRSCnWS6_nYAgL4K6eJK2ihjk0fyZQW4UI8zTSdNkQJfL69YQngAni1Iyq0=]. These strong global engagement metrics for the 'It's kind of delicious and wonderful' campaign contrast with the reported U.S. volume decline, indicating a need for more granular, localized analysis of channel performance and conversion in key markets [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEjmvxo82V1HS4XOI4o1VHkqoworV9mdbZsiLB3FrhJizpRVs2i20YE9WCUqmMeazXonfzHqB10OGXXdWP2yg6veH69zboVtXBdcJ3ePrV3nSpPud015cDvm5Xu28I_GaHf1IvVfRa6JDF_wH7ZB0Nu1WLcdziIhgsK7MBlkETnyEpNqmmSJ_EeT-lUjfdaUIk=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHA8DKwb6zYoP6MKPq4mRTcpHirt0JxoBqYMkds1UqogfWgUknlUpFYcSpPUH0OiZGkK5YX4apx7NbBxMJw2jM4LXonst0mT0Ux6fiIZ_9mZmBtI8gxHIQ3GUUTb1HDyTcnVgDcJNXhs8cRaiH13ZfPLG2j8TwUedzV6MHJZXX0rp3-E=].\n\nIn January 2025, Glenmorangie launched a multi-year global marketing campaign **'Once Upon a Time in Scotland' starring Harrison Ford** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHF-n57G-dPjLph3l7JZR58k0u-YfgB1LfQDc7MZ8kLfMCGRlzga-pR2IkojoePnzFIlMQi8S6FVuuQX123BDKJVnNDvemQh2DLfwARSXdrXNdK4uXfkZpOS-OmQV47DAFNPQ5ARWxgmtMILHInYDMzzDiU1SCb8-MUbMtRcJDdjJMYUYgdUZF4jVc, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEBkMLngaKQPTCnLk5cvMP4vkKI8xXzsW-GLkIvcBTaCa8tsEESwZuhb7HlPBPwd5AL4tmL5KbeoG-7F4hon_N1LNkadivnpSTC_99xACp-snfn4qTpnYtXvi28IdOnEFBqfYPz4DqGOkyArRfdeLoaz0eZiwQMbIh5DddFMzzE8w0diWw==]. This campaign, featuring a 12-episode series directed by Joel Edgerton, aims to make single malt Scotch feel less formal and more emotionally accessible, leveraging Ford's global appeal to reach new premium spirits consumers, particularly in growth markets like India [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQETYSs2oZ5OlHj42g6bcqZSAWpQux5iDyxzZR414RCGtZ_3cHV5WpEF3uaKTK3nI-GrIwvaaAnyGpn_XDcJr8QrGk9PoMMrUAp6OFFO3y_dTKg0dUnBGAaKYX9WECOCrnqd_trnnH9Jy7MHEiDiUiifmcOuLE05X9xg5QhGTqZzqMsM5sESd6rmcrTyEnEtcAZ457_BZWNttcFiog==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGvryFkTm8VABNU6jinnau_BfnTYU8mnCTU0GQX0wBH_jgSQDXDRozTquqBb4aKsmahY4UFFIS-8_0PK4i91qilWtG3YLx24V73fySZBNcvUX6HwCN17gc1_twzg2Pish0ZJrq1NmQW-5v9oVwFv056iBkvnQEeB6WbPiY7C1OtfCMGhmeVMzQUQbz0jdZ8Q==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGh3SLUyZgu58dWkx75gGGCoeiOifRVplt_kDhtq00XKXqovYNqo5M4T-DquoZz8ecFyxLX6cNbg_qzqd3pZlwvWWllEoXhiK-2QlQXAlnuB8Oz0Q3MLq7Dt5KIo5-WUMf5CbD8v0cCBM8Kedx54dCMnKH_l2x3HZ_8G57V3rT-I6OF5z5t9Jml8QOPUWhpLVu0HB3g-i_F4M4tp8WvdTbJqOb5udjpOsN1kH76eiyCkRLjRz3bgKAKvvsmuTnlQG8HYxfIb6KMOYk==]. In May 2026, a new product, the **'Glenmorangie Harrison Ford Limited Edition,'** a custom blend primarily ex-bourbon barrel aged with a finish in toasted Portuguese red wine casks, was announced in conjunction with Ford [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHF-n57G-dPjLph3l7JZR58k0u-YfgB1LfQDc7MZ8kLfMCGRlzga-pR2IkojoePnzFIlMQi8S6FVuuQX123BDKJVnNDvemQh2DLfwARSXdrXNdK4uXfkZpOS-OmQV47DAFNPQ5ARWxgmtMILHInYDMzzDiU1SCb8-MUbMtRcJDdjJMYUYgdUZF4jVc, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGrM7wSYBrYoiVs1WFloSLXBIbR2GUrFr_KVc3Mldw6uVg3HlHUCY9Dd4NpSj_DdEapIoKGQaQsPlGvmiFtiQTnIcirpgwamVkRelXQTsP4UVcV7oQfBkH1decFZHhC7em7cMQkZL3uZUD6zZZu6HD6OeXjs4lpKNyydBbQfxWF3hcFGwNivsVZR2JDTI-z8HmvlSBMu1WBL2VLuPdPQv5wmUGN7wNE2D45vd_69nOCwc5KEVyY-HEHU8ELE0bjM3MdqFXeIDrx-WE=].\n\nGlenmorangie became the **official whisky partner of Formula One** in 2025 [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHF-n57G-dPjLph3l7JZR58k0u-YfgB1LfQDc7MZ8kLfMCGRlzga-pR2IkojoePnzFIlMQi8S6FVuuQX123BDKJVnNDvemQh2DLfwARSXdrXNdK4uXfkZpOS-OmQV47DAFNPQ5ARWxgmtMILHInYDMzzDiU1SCb8-MUbMtRcJDdjJMYUYgdUZF4jVc, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGdnx5ITl2gDjlgbHdspbVdXyZH0pIQWqCwJZacINR86OzFemtv8ExMnuBjxfxpJJJgx2a6-PtwENXWD3h0Gxq00pcbBDTQMs3wAP7BnDytgW-1bd37yM1-MDK_WP9ALm2TDeo6bJGtYHkCJXGR7TJslBViCxuLiQY5ZfHMpt-BsV6F34BibE5w-9CvO_7UunqG9wB6hd3RfbCwAltq9c14tB82C_j4fx0r]. The 'A Tale of Tokyo' limited-edition series received a **Double Gold award** at the San Francisco World Spirits Competition 2023 [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEi9lYrwyU82dLhxuZQ1S-2StdT2WHilNgokJWbJIFtRFi8LEClEJaiEUCGqs3G1WDicojYphBnVIsp2xC7aehCF5g7smSDVNXdLj6cuLBsOHpbFkib97P4Ny1e_drGvsW5GXhNY2pyrskTCNCAjYW9yWDdbB5U-l5aIHkyHsPfzvKXJhrz_AHiz833RvU6-0a3Yec2n0QQOCkIdqY8d6cWmDLMnGOFYhe9CePGwmEQiWLevifesFFQcwKb, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEfG6ZDFBd6bFhzIS1_DsHxbdu3zlqu9BsGy3ublzvLOSl93_z1HOQAGpA2As2SuD8d8OmkEXKH0mipapghaUhGApsffMzj0ee-vEu3hznGOXS-R5PWhGGlUxVgyzRWnMkRoWtV-5g5jcceP8YPxvo8rtCkBvqxr66uS0Sxo1kGI8IMDARWYFO2fdc=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFYlcSIVbl2fefAv1ISD0Ei94mc6kBMjf6KD8Bfi09Vy6CuG1KSfxxYY7dgNMs4wwiEifuuAUHLhaYhWSkzzPPAN-_6LQSPI5gzU03nNuMbWTxNhx0wBZlo9zWAPySXI7ZQKzDx2zF0GbQWKgTCmI1NJOwIAtVz].\n\n---\n\n"},{"level":2,"title":"6. Current Strategy","content":"\nGlenmorangie is actively pursuing a **premiumization strategy** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHF-n57G-dPjLph3l7JZR58k0u-YfgB1LfQDc7MZ8kLfMCGRlzga-pR2IkojoePnzFIlMQi8S6FVuuQX123BDKJVnNDvemQh2DLfwARSXdrXNdK4uXfkZpOS-OmQV47DAFNPQ5ARWxgmtMILHInYDMzzDiU1SCb8-MUbMtRcJDdjJMYUYgdUZF4jVc, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGdnx5ITl2gDjlgbHdspbVdXyZH0pIQWqCwJZacINR86OzFemtv8ExMnuBjxfxpJJJgx2a6-PtwENXWD3h0Gxq00pcbBDTQMs3wAP7BnDytgW-1bd37yM1-MDK_WP9ALm2TDeo6bJGtYHkCJXGR7TJslBViCxuLiQY5ZfHMpt-BsV6F34BibE5w-9CvO_7UunqG9wB6hd3RfbCwAltq9c14tB82C_j4fx0r]. This is evidenced by several recent product updates:\n*   In 2024, Glenmorangie increased the age statement of **The Original from 10 to 12 years** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHF-n57G-dPjLph3l7JZR58k0u-YfgB1LfQDc7MZ8kLfMCGRlzga-pR2IkojoePnzFIlMQi8S6FVuuQX123BDKJVnNDvemQh2DLfwARSXdrXNdK4uXfkZpOS-OmQV47DAFNPQ5ARWxgmtMILHInYDMzzDiU1SCb8-MUbMtRcJDdjJMYUYgdUZF4jVc, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFcoQwFr2HQfgYQTnON7tekXIHns8_r40ExSc0Z78cg3NowtHvvNuZFSLTNqVS9BlDu8zZ7RHoyCo6HcjtLYPV5RXhaB8DxRkbhTvZcgqHZFYaRFNY9NqGqFqXLPHbKnMRxb2UqwqloRedOribzHHBUqn7nmxIrmilgYYr5_7SaCwygrcwPdS1J0bNM5ZStPw==]. Concurrently, the ABV for The Original shifted from 43% to 40% [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHF-n57G-dPjLph3l7JZR58k0u-YfgB1LfQDc7MZ8kLfMCGRlzga-pR2IkojoePnzFIlMQi8S6FVuuQX123BDKJVnNDvemQh2DLfwARSXdrXNdK4uXfkZpOS-OmQV47DAFNPQ5ARWxgmtMILHInYDMzzDiU1SCb8-MUbMtRcJDdjJMYUYgdUZF4jVc, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFcoQwFr2HQfgYQTnON7tekXIHns8_r40ExSc0Z78cg3NowtHvvNuZFSLTNqVS9BlDu8zZ7RHoyCo6HcjtLYPV5RXhaB8DxRkbhTvZcgqHZFYaRFNY9NqGqFqXLPHbKnMRxb2UqwqloRedOribzHHBUqn7nmxIrmilgYYr5_7SaCwygrcwPdS1J0bNM5ZStPw==].\n*   In March 2025, The Lasanta's age statement increased from 12 to **15 years** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHF-n57G-dPjLph3l7JZR58k0u-YfgB1LfQDc7MZ8kLfMCGRlzga-pR2IkojoePnzFIlMQi8S6FVuuQX123BDKJVnNDvemQh2DLfwARSXdrXNdK4uXfkZpOS-OmQV47DAFNPQ5ARWxgmtMILHInYDMzzDiU1SCb8-MUbMtRcJDdjJMYUYgdUZF4jVc, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEtpYAIkHYN0cLccP0pme694lUuYVcLMRop6CyswnmY2AeIbZ0w2jTICBPP-DvjMCtUGnklb2DzIZ51tV-FtzpTTPIEd_LPEkVKGlt3SMyLbno_v73vLJkvBSIifhyhjhumE3ihELGiMvsp7EKM5s4eBN2_c3CEmSZDxhIs390Bwd_ZipEJrEUS9LdwPj9n2AsyJcVwd1q3fw==].\n*   In 2023, The Nectar was upgraded from a non-age statement to a **16-year-old expression** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHF-n57G-dPjLph3l7JZR58k0u-YfgB1LfQDc7MZ8kLfMCGRlzga-pR2IkojoePnzFIlMQi8S6FVuuQX123BDKJVnNDvemQh2DLfwARSXdrXNdK4uXfkZpOS-OmQV47DAFNPQ5ARWxgmtMILHInYDMzzDiU1SCb8-MUbMtRcJDdjJMYUYgdUZF4jVc, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGEx53pQLYXnaFNBoQt1V3F8wumXPatJmLNzOaE0YzartLmhPMLD_xmU5ezIWEIaRMNgI_bfcT1i-IuzaTjhj-dRTSpB0RIcwXB0AxMLGlRtTZglD8Yv_czrbSSFPIZ_3lM8SpaJ_uwryhHoirrbBjieFegPZuEtCbM1jfaENbCcxpKainkiHS5PTJcrdIdgD9QRBD3im3tDZc2nia08yDmpGHLzA==].\n*   In March 2026, Glenmorangie launched **'The Thirty,' a 30-year-old single malt**, as its oldest core expression, retailing at £740 (US$989/€850) [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHF-n57G-dPjLph3l7JZR58k0u-YfgB1LfQDc7MZ8kLfMCGRlzga-pR2IkojoePnzFIlMQi8S6FVuuQX123BDKJVnNDvemQh2DLfwARSXdrXNdK4uXfkZpOS-OmQV47DAFNPQ5ARWxgmtMILHInYDMzzDiU1SCb8-MUbMtRcJDdjJMYUYgdUZF4jVc, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHsnGqMh1NBmnds2kymCEje14bbZoy5JdGaiBICiFhnHuT_VW-MJSIY1RMPdklC0wl0XJvdOMj3HAvw_vJNB23P9S5Lk9RGR_yIO7rvCC5tdyBHw11ATGgtlm5PKiuHe7qfM0yX77sZLgTOyc3tfBTAC5L1_Rl8bR-AiDV2S9TTk63zp54ZqtOc1gwgLDV4WT9QWBXF0Gh0CK2wGPnU10TYtmG4nPH6DtEyHrz2nkf2dzuhmJkfXM4=].\n\nGlenmorangie continues to innovate with limited editions, launching **'A Tale of Ice Cream'** in 2024 and **'A Tale of Spices'** (featuring a four-cask finish including Moroccan red wine casks) in 2025 [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHF-n57G-dPjLph3l7JZR58k0u-YfgB1LfQDc7MZ8kLfMCGRlzga-pR2IkojoePnzFIlMQi8S6FVuuQX123BDKJVnNDvemQh2DLfwARSXdrXNdK4uXfkZpOS-OmQV47DAFNPQ5ARWxgmtMILHInYDMzzDiU1SCb8-MUbMtRcJDdjJMYUYgdUZF4jVc, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGdnx5ITl2gDjlgbHdspbVdXyZH0pIQWqCwJZacINR86OzFemtv8ExMnuBjxfxpJJJgx2a6-PtwENXWD3h0Gxq00pcbBDTQMs3wAP7BnDytgW-1bd37yM1-MDK_WP9ALm2TDeo6bJGtYHkCJXGR7TJslBViCxuLiQY5ZfHMpt-BsV6F34BibE5w-9CvO_7UunqG9wB6hd3RfbCwAltq9c14tB82C_j4fx0r]. In 2025, 'The Altus 25 Years Old,' a single malt matured in Bourbon and finished in Madeira wine casks, was unveiled [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHF-n57G-dPjLph3l7JZR58k0u-YfgB1LfQDc7MZ8kLfMCGRlzga-pR2IkojoePnzFIlMQi8S6FVuuQX123BDKJVnNDvemQh2DLfwARSXdrXNdK4uXfkZpOS-OmQV47DAFNPQ5ARWxgmtMILHInYDMzzDiU1SCb8-MUbMtRcJDdjJMYUYgdUZF4jVc, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGdnx5ITl2gDjlgbHdspbVdXyZH0pIQWqCwJZacINR86OzFemtv8ExMnuBjxfxpJJJgx2a6-PtwENXWD3h0Gxq00pcbBDTQMs3wAP7BnDytgW-1bd37yM1-MDK_WP9ALm2TDeo6bJGtYHkCJXGR7TJslBViCxuLiQY5ZfHMpt-BsV6F34BibE5w-9CvO_7UunqG9wB6hd3RfbCwAltq9c14tB82C_j4fx0r]. The **Lighthouse experimental distillery**, dedicated solely to experimentation and taste innovation, opened in September 2021 [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHF-n57G-dPjLph3l7JZR58k0u-YfgB1LfQDc7MZ8kLfMCGRlzga-pR2IkojoePnzFIlMQi8S6FVuuQX123BDKJVnNDvemQh2DLfwARSXdrXNdK4uXfkZpOS-OmQV47DAFNPQ5ARWxgmtMILHInYDMzzDiU1SCb8-MUbMtRcJDdjJMYUYgdUZF4jVc, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGdnx5ITl2gDjlgbHdspbVdXyZH0pIQWqCwJZacINR86OzFemtv8ExMnuBjxfxpJJJgx2a6-PtwENXWD3h0Gxq00pcbBDTQMs3wAP7BnDytgW-1bd37yM1-MDK_WP9ALm2TDeo6bJGtYHkCJXGR7TJslBViCxuLiQY5ZfHMpt-BsV6F34BibE5w-9CvO_7UunqG9wB6hd3RfbCwAltq9c14tB82C_j4fx0r].\n\nGlenmorangie's marketing efforts are focused on **global expansion and making single malt Scotch more approachable** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHF-n57G-dPjLph3l7JZR58k0u-YfgB1LfQDc7MZ8kLfMCGRlzga-pR2IkojoePnzFIlMQi8S6FVuuQX123BDKJVnNDvemQh2DLfwARSXdrXNdK4uXfkZpOS-OmQV47DAFNPQ5ARWxgmtMILHInYDMzzDiU1SCb8-MUbMtRcJDdjJMYUYgdUZF4jVc, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEBkMLngaKQPTCnLk5cvMP4vkKI8xXzsW-GLkIvcBTaCa8tsEESwZuhb7HlPBPwd5AL4tmL5KbeoG-7F4hon_N1LNkadivnpSTgYu6DIZx-99xACp-snfn4qTpnYtXvi28IdOnEFBqfYPz4DqGOkyArRfdeLoaz0eZiwQMbIh5DddFMzzE8w0diWw==]. The 'X by Glenmorangie' bottling, launched in 2021, was specifically targeted at clubs and Gen Z drinkers, designed for mixing into cocktails [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEQaozRBkxp4zmuWtJyojpfPxg55evjZVzLfcH-hQVNNisYntjTeIgfe9MX8Zz6KRlsC4z3yflzUw8oagzI2R6CCkKFpf45RFcv8VLG0-ej5zpeLl6p7hwSxWBRIOHxX1fa-BNKH1jDeZZt, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGZwdlveioCQ5431dzA0XzPfzYWEtPsgfcm74_33DBbD_sFF1Q76JiL8vaRKuaS_iCYoa9xWe9xrxNQjrLBaB1ZoJX2Vmt1D66isOE6ROu1tFOL1TE7yl9TvkOdnsnVsuQf-HOr69FFe9PhR7LeQOrRQVgjwPk01Jc4BeMj2Ot1LIK42P0SLit-eeXU58RCeIc73GkFYhDz6jOcU94Ahczft6LIpCJ-ib31cP8JjViuPylZZIaogQ==].\n\n---\n\n"},{"level":2,"title":"7. Performance","content":"\nGlenmorangie recorded its **'best ever sales performance' in 2021** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG2oTqFUtysDVV6B1mtpyT56Yu8ZNBG-13UlMuUd-EtX_0D1O7cjgtCML_BN17gkc5PpqBaf-inW3nwBg2N4vqrtEZ9BvZSqeKBZ4fYSZ57xje2ti4K89g5ehp7KvSTdofFAvZJM-Dr4RnNmYq51Q5YJJQArV2CxmL96K3YuIlh2QwMHgHKCrqyDol36GM-gxOdCMLzYrVepRX24abD05D0YS7Q64t0U_wY, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG2P6qlY_YdNfmR8Zn9gqwzIEE9eP8GTDLdty7qzzO03IT_Xaa0lqJ4RRFQ1LU0v_uFuq_HE6tapvqmCM2dwucqhzE57VYaYFT4ES3CLD0TjY6Lt4MBezIP7fXq2O9mkX9z7fBPQwV6Sh6jzv087X9-o2eC2NexqNAlfGZMfNlaT925WG2Plw3OWlKt3ubkHBYG9yTg56LOPHSLELQyezIXF8Ky]. Global demand for Glenmorangie was reported to be **'growing significantly' in September 2021** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFnFaSXp8Z-9Ga6T0BuzZ-1BOVYP4eIz3uqPigoIdmgD3eUs_W54SNL5lqwwWCURkGqnp8N5pMvzK9nGF3_CNRQvt3wDhvgYYN73DHK-X_R1AQwiIODHWQXsoa2yEdzKZ3m3a_q949rIRyrErceriBSryEpBZrkeAIGRy0QxvBFS9YLglwlow==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG2P6qlY_YdNfmR8Zn9gqwzIEE9eP8GTDLdty7qzzO03IT_Xaa0lqJ4RRFQ1LU0v_uFuq_HE6tapvqmCM2dwucqhzE57VYaYFT4ES3CLD0TjY6Lt4MBezIP7fXq2O9mkX9z7fBPQwV6Sh6jzv087X9-o2eC2NexqNAlfGZMfNlaT925WG2Plw3OWlKt3ubkHBYG9yTg56LOPHSLELQyezIXF8Ky].\n\nHowever, Glenmorangie's U.S. sales volume declined by **30.5% from 128,000 9-liter cases in 2022 to 89,000 cases in 2023** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHF-n57G-dPjLph3l7JZR58k0u-YfgB1LfQDc7MZ8kLfMCGRlzga-pR2IkojoePnzFIlMQi8S6FVuuQX123BDKJVnNDvemQh2DLfwARSXdrXNdK4uXfkZpOS-OmQV47DAFNPQ5ARWxgmtMILHInYDMzzDiU1SCb8-MUbMtRcJDdjJMYUYgdUZF4jVc, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEoUy37puSGEHD54KCxuHxNiLp3IpOx6jbbF21KS0ViosX2-dKh4Iww6lZnQFSxcFk7nGrzrFk8I6PwzojmwcTqv1FeCEqwqIoN9Af9yjpvrcXxitgKnWFFwRIHX5snlH-IhZULHVDo36JNDwwOPl-IqwZgfQ==]. Despite this volume decline, its value remained relatively consistent [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEBSqrgLfrFsxr0kxCR-J2gVvUpCzslCbSWa1Xc-tMCQ5VjUNXyc1HGWe-gCo41c4cfMU4HbyGdt9vHtK4ejqNBk8nafmdjg0SYpluNFVPSGOQZzNCXPJcDcyzx4oY_yvMHpS1SXzQOh4v6meaKcnkmr5XumCzDW4Y0JHZ_C0zS, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG_wKOsWXndjb0lVObnmENZg7W9dbYuSsEW84vpy6CmXMFxFfGB3nGHrPmxDx38_NsoBbzABv46qCvEwwf3u2bUH-OTu8HQP2WsEivBHejZas1Z5NPoZMv2GGvVWD2kHhLuTVpUZxenZVR937JA_tPx-QuyEz2z7ZCE4o6tCM3v5sqmn93lqD9xEWA==]. Glenmorangie's U.S. volume was approximately **90,000 cases in January 2025** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG2P6qlY_YdNfmR8Zn9gqwzIEE9eP8GTDLdty7qzzO03IT_Xaa0lqJ4RRFQ1LU0v_uFuq_HE6tapvqmCM2dwucqhzE57VYaYFT4ES3CLD0TjY6Lt4MBezIP7fXq2O9mkX9z7fBPQwV6Sh6jzv087X9-o2eC2NexqNAlfGZMfNlaT925WG2Plw3OWlKt3ubkHBYG9yTg56LOPHSLELQyezIXF8Ky, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH8fVH-lrzCKufp1cJTQd_xafFLoQpoU5nflLwbTK9viXyvA4ThLCWfz2GnbqBrihuA1OZ4GY2HIvQBW376VOF8QiIV7KojclyiXMA1XSV2hLpImzY7VJ3DfLHF4XpwwKtnIcsgsQlbaJdqajBmpBvpRNIU5LPeXWtRUtc=]. The U.S. Scotch whisky market experienced a significant decline in 2024, with **single malt Scotch volumes declining by 17% and value by 14%**, and blended Scotch volumes declining by 14% and value by 15% [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHRo0oaBCJGo-Di_NZVLMNSZfnJq1ONCzfLrDiIjVXselPv2_zKQxTCF70YVBJI0jQ2tNgykqvgTVZuQUHqJuWWxVsKKaLaqMc96aqeicGT0SglWE36lvcn73b9GqKfpK11iX7W_YyblWLE-49NGmnuZ1MDkVvmQpK6Rtc_9S2yh0KgQ3g4OQ8XV-pXQnA-DT3Txu-UFfZOQIioAQK_tnIE5eGQfWjpuZkF7Q14Cg=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFGqmZ4UK3SlL1pyMQ_Q7nI52OAme8D47GiuWlIcz39R5_HJ9SVFmsGpXBaNUhG3tF46OMhcPPqz0f0UEheiv3Lrp9Car6aZAdosqBEUPPmW6u-YccnF7WdkyJIE3zbLJpvTzARWssqN6Gcf1J6VMGGINSJUaE7YwuJdypQt1_1Drab2b8buk2vHD02YSSwdJPDDF4W].\n\nGlenmorangie is a top-selling global single malt brand, ranking as the **4th top-selling global single malt with 540,000 9-liter cases** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEBSqrgLfrFsxr0kxCR-J2gVvUpCzslCbSWa1Xc-tMCQ5VjUNXyc1HGWe-gCo41c4cfMU4HbyGdt9vHtK4ejqNBk8nafmdjg0SYpluNFVPSGOQZzNCXPJcDcyzx4oY_yvMHpS1SXzQOh4v6meaKcnkmr5XumCzDW4Y0JHZ_C0zS, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGSBuhdTeVCmZynT8NMnSHYkoUVag69GDnVIOPUTGPY3zt8fEXa1g2H4LNtQzwts087QbxQc-NbIwGX-KxtEG71fRtadJM9pPkHnG3WbJY7UmxGuzUQFKMRLroYlBOYb2pJphQkx8Em1AGl_64ir1YxxZyroWMDvcKDyz48FKPdl8QSNNb4Hfvy3A==]. It is considered the **world's fourth or fifth best-selling single malt as of March 2024** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG2P6qlY_YdNfmR8Zn9gqwzIEE9eP8GTDLdty7qzzO03IT_Xaa0lqJ4RRFQ1LU0v_uFuq_HE6tapvqmCM2dwucqhzE57VYaYFT4ES3CLD0TjY6Lt4MBezIP7fXq2O9mkX9z7fBPQwV6Sh6jzv087X9-o2eC2NexqNAlfGZMfNlaT925WG2Plw3OWlKt3ubkHBYG9yTg56LOPHSLELQyezIXF8Ky, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH6XcqQnZtuuHtOsF1wNxemkTXEiE7FnPn7rhRDb2Ec91KTNHqa4Lne3JnywizA-q8hK7Bo__bMx6LvvHMcT9OE1IAkm2wNNZKrdXxloZJNCzgWnMYJ_0RIdmihHGHnzOcXYUSUu9qiaFeTtBPd9KP_7wwFf6weBWQWHLO456mb5WtjvEcs0COm3X1e2M8YtA==], holding a **6% share of the global single malt market as of 2025** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG2P6qlY_YdNfmR8Zn9gqwzIEE9eP8GTDLdty7qzzO03IT_Xaa0lqJ4RRFQ1LU0v_uFuq_HE6tapvqmCM2dwucqhzE57VYaYFT4ES3CLD0TjY6Lt4MBezIP7fXq2O9mkX9z7fBPQwV6Sh6jzv087X9-o2eC2NexqNAlfGZMfNlaT925WG2Plw3OWlKt3ubkHBYG9yTg56LOPHSLELQyezIXF8Ky, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGIoeKDoCsc5adNZUBdZD1Q0wl_LoOTfSmSxm-h-5HqznWTCYn0TraNYRT9k6J9OeVkPuKgI6bV17i0o_E6riMVqFngK6iYRL0N-_CsfkMXAnd3sqNFhmq0Wv-NWP-fcIeGqZ-rlyU7hqRe7UYD5YIoWG8rY7lAFfFtRM7vj58LWydYPb8ShdV6Ug==] with estimated annual sales of **7 million bottles** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG2P6qlY_YdNfmR8Zn9gqwzIEE9eP8GTDLdty7qzzO03IT_Xaa0lqJ4RRFQ1LU0v_uFuq_HE6tapvqmCM2dwucqhzE57VYaYFT4ES3CLD0TjY6Lt4MBezIP7fXq2O9mkX9z7fBPQwV6Sh6jzv087X9-o2eC2NexqNAlfGZMfNlaT925WG2Plw3OWlKt3ubkHBYG9yTg56LOPHSLELQyezIXF8Ky, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGIoeKDoCsc5adNZUBdZD1Q0wl_LoOTfSmSxm-h-5HqznWTCYn0TraNYRT9k6J9OeVkPuKgI6bV17i0o_E6riMVqFngK6iYRL0N-_CsfkMXAnd3sqNFhmq0Wv-NWP-fcIeGqZ-rlyU7hqRe7UYD5YIoWG8rY7lAFfFtRM7vj58LWydYPb8ShdV6Ug==].\n\nLVMH's Wines & Spirits division, which includes Glenmorangie, experienced an **8% organic revenue drop in 2024 to €5.862 billion** [https://www.lvmh.com/news-documents/press-releases/lvmh-full-year-2024-results/, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2025/01/lvmh-wines-spirits-revenue-drops-8-in-2024/]. This was followed by a further **5% organic revenue decline in 2025 to €5.358 billion** (full-year) [https://www.lvmh.com/news-documents/press-releases/lvmh-first-half-2025-results/, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2025/07/lvmh-wines-spirits-revenue-down-5-in-h1-2025/]. Profit from recurring operations for the division fell by **25% in 2025 compared to 2024** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG2P6qlY_YdNfmR8Zn9gqwzIEE9eP8GTDLdty7qzzO03IT_Xaa0lqJ4RRFQ1LU0v_uFuq_HE6tapvqmCM2dwucqhzE57VYaYFT4ES3CLD0TjY6Lt4MBezIP7fXq2O9mkX9z7fBPQwV6Sh6jzv087X9-o2eC2NexqNAlfGZMfNlaT925WG2Plw3OWlKt3ubkHBYG9yTg56LOPHSLELQyezIXF8Ky, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGIoeKDoCsc5adNZUBdZD1Q0wl_LoOTfSmSxm-h-5HqznWTCYn0TraNYRT9k6J9OeVkPuKgI6bV17i0o_E6riMVqFngK6iYRL0N-_CsfkMXAnd3sqNFhmq0Wv-NWP-fcIeGqZ-rlyU7hqRe7UYD5YIoWG8rY7lAFfFtRM7vj58LWydYPb8ShdV6Ug==]. For the first 9 months of 2025, revenue was **€3.92 billion**, compared to €4.19 billion in 2024 (9 months), an organic decline of 4% with a 2% negative currency effect [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG2P6qlY_YdNfmR8Zn9gqwzIEE9eP8GTDLdty7qzzO03IT_Xaa0lqJ4RRFQ1LU0v_uFuq_HE6tapvqmCM2dwucqhzE57VYaYFT4ES3CLD0TjY6Lt4MBezIP7fXq2O9mkX9z7fBPQwV6Sh6jzv087X9-o2eC2NexqNAlfGZMfNlaT925WG2Plw3OWlKt3ubkHBYG9yTg56LOPHSLELQyezIXF8Ky, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGIoeKDoCsc5adNZUBdZD1Q0wl_LoOTfSmSxm-h-5HqznWTCYn0TraNYRT9k6J9OeVkPuKgI6bV17i0o_E6riMVqFngK6iYRL0N-_CsfkMXAnd3sqNFhmq0Wv-NWP-fcIeGqZ-rlyU7hqRe7UYD5YIoWG8rY7lAFfFtRM7vj58LWydYPb8ShdV6Ug==]. However, Q3 2025 showed **+1% organic growth**, signaling early signs of stabilization [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG2P6qlY_YdNfmR8Zn9gqwzIEE9eP8GTDLdty7qzzO03IT_Xaa0lqJ4RRFQ1LU0v_uFuq_HE6tapvqmCM2dwucqhzE57VYaYFT4ES3CLD0TjY6Lt4MBezIP7fXq2O9mkX9z7fBPQwV6Sh6jzv087X9-o2eC2NexqNAlfGZMfNlaT925WG2Plw3OWlKt3ubkHBYG9yTg56LOPHSLELQyezIXF8Ky, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGIoeKDoCsc5adNZUBdZD1Q0wl_LoOTfSmSxm-h-5HqznWTCYn0TraNYRT9k6J9OeVkPuKgI6bV17i0o_E6riMVqFngK6iYRL0N-_CsfkMXAnd3sqNFhmq0Wv-NWP-fcIeGqZ-rlyU7hqRe7UYD5YIoWG8rY7lAFfFtRM7vj58LWydYPb8ShdV6Ug==]. LVMH's Wines & Spirits division experienced a **12% organic revenue decline in Q1 2024** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGAo4K-N9JWPQp9j5hY5inBfKuP6i1HNhprfGbt8Xqb_cC0VfDJDKQL4wF00XtnTWUkWmMG_gRIs8uSfIzw38dyFfN81TA5FYcwJtpZ-uJCgmfXGvPYOprPnQDrFh6tQKe2Ar1mqBnCO4gR9QbzDEDT68n16i-_Tsp0jPg9GhbXPkmY0kp84_g1UocUfTSSwPEqAv_5w==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGFJFGBTqhMS5Xy_U03b5vqHiAUi8FDk_GZbOigMsziVsSHvNPj4BvblIfJWy0titGXPPbH-gNvujo1U7Rkv3Q9EjSrb3c6mIyrLXfAe7ynOdNtioM112IJHn6iEpFpn97f6O16LTo_IZe9k2CJW0vl9WjGF3MUpG6mVzJKnKsEycDoslnxJoUP-IeL-8Kl8u30GPMBbeks88-DHA==] and a **14% drop in profits year-over-year for H1 2024** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGFJFGBTqhMS5Xy_U03b3vqHiAUi8FDk_GZbOigMsziVsSHvNPj4BvblIfJWy0titGXPPbH-gNvujo1U7Rkv3Q9EjSrb3c6mIyrLXfAe7ynOdNtioM112IJHn6iEpFpn97f6O16LTo_IZe9k2CJW0vl9WjGF3MUpG6mVzJKnKsEycDoslnxJoUP-IeL-8Kl8u30GPMBbeks88-DHA==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH8Z4IB511A2IjWnMYTnLoFdBbJyU095e8qiz2LodvehZx2h5PJNDy4j9tBKSzFLuBTXG1tMXEs-m1aZIZ1A6ebkYo43z-S2NkjxI6Gsd5fwyRY5I85SIuvACcXr1gO83wD0j0YTz26F6_7yY0kp1S10D_k5aELZk5sR7VPz7dJ3urWnMiFO6cC3qGMK0E=].\n\nGlenmorangie was recognized as a **'house pour' in 8% of bars** surveyed for the Drinks International Brands Report 2024, and a **'second bestseller' in 4% of bars** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG2P6qlY_YdNfmR8Zn9gqwzIEE9eP8GTDLdty7qzzO03IT_Xaa0lqJ4RRFQ1LU0v_uFuq_HE6tapvqmCM2dwucqhzE57VYaYFT4ES3CLD0TjY6Lt4MBezIP7fXq2O9mkX9z7fBPQwV6Sh6jzv087X9-o2eC2NexqNAlfGZMfNlaT925WG2Plw3OWlKt3ubkHBYG9yTg56LOPHSLELQyezIXF8Ky, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFnvZfn4wNJVmLwZ0izsuW2pNySJKyHwhVdw1XFKQfu95f_ACLTDK45Lwrbb9nLE_MJcdKEZQBgXUqZtgiBhR4kkCKcwZiFcuBtrZlwc9zVUDhyOsLkIGPp_-9mbTC82RE3kxPx4AH8RYG7-mI-ea4NouF3-I7WE3-Ey53svRESLQJp-fyNFa7kkcs3toWmZKR7umh5].\n\n---\n\n"},{"level":2,"title":"8. Profitability Pools & White-Space Opportunities","content":"\nGlenmorangie operates within the highly profitable premium and luxury spirits segments, which are experiencing significant growth. The global premium spirits market was valued between **USD 223.90 billion and USD 253.77 billion in 2025** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGARRn77bFWyAondYf8ioHil914Gnpt_TueA099GTj64Y918HKCwBaN4MzFoKqJtpUDcCxR03R6SoPNZfqo9EwqmYK02wPFZ93oih6Z16ObH5a8_yk9S2UrY97zwutOA0LrtQv2emV6wKdyLmB4lmlTbR3izxgJy0puLtu8NFYnTQ==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFFD0QVoO9MQ22f--O8IQJ86GtCRn--4i1Rn6xVXN2AtWGY6ducy1cZ996Eh2c_upMAxgG_Z3p6ivnaV__0jKjFaFtXT21wuMSh47vBq6LOnAqHz8rGAInPMM3lUDgNZr1F4mSNbUxtRUP-s3vSkuC8DBkFXTTwm0MRxrnx9RCSBqkw3AI=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEVaDwPWV3_wDiZgP0xJ6U5Z0N6s7aXglGda-_7pE-iXvgrc7231GZ-EnODVNdi43Ty1ActTIUU6SREpUX7LPB8gy2x3Z1idDKLEjntts02ASUkr3CXDhDdMFpTdqioh1Bq6v26IEgyWGQEuImaGY5shcZgNgZU5WTiqfXoZHG2_5UoMkk=] and is projected to grow at a CAGR of **6.37% (2026-2034) or 10.3% (2026-2033)** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGARRn77bFWyAondYf8ioHil914Gnpt_TueA099GTj64Y918HKCwBaN4MzFoKqJtpUDcCxR03R6SoPNZfqo9EwqmYK02wPFZ93oih6Z16ObH5a8_yk9S2UrY97zwutOA0LrtQv2emV6wKdyLmB4lmlTbR3izxgJy0puLtu8NFYnTQ==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFFD0QVoO9MQ22f--O8IQJ86GtCRn--4i1Rn6xVXN2AtWGY6ducy1cZ996Eh2c_upMAxgG_Z3p6ivnaV__0jKjFaFtXT21wuMSh47vBq6LOnAqHz8rGAInPMM3lUDgNZr1F4mSNbUxtRUP-s3vSkuC8DBkFXTTwm0MRxrnx9RCSBqkw3AI=]. The luxury spirits market, a sub-segment, was valued at **USD 71.09 billion in 2025** and is expected to reach **USD 189.48 billion by 2035**, growing at a CAGR of **10.3% from 2026 to 2035** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGI-SovfXXUCwb6aQ6iV8PmZ5mqf0DG_1No2D7pZZER4N1pe9GxtPQBn_DgJvPsMKhNxrDgIzkjO1yKB33J1CnwteSOPHENZ8GIEelEvdbpt4ngOt2k42M0Pph6FkBCrzHmwZVAo0w_t31LO2qslmM774veh_Qy-fKoOQWURQl-tO5TJ4ssjbiA_eh7, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHf6Vp5_FhbBoNMsqGfsnFkfXyMhwg3b1d2S8owRR8ZGuMM0mL2A58l0sSk6vxNtS7NsFoFv0LDuSZ5HLgA3zK6Zqcz02xhv0uvodZzrEYggobxnwiQESSSIkS6AVTJufkgC9wYgHFbD8OHhNXRva7j]. Glenmorangie's premiumization strategy, increasing age statements and introducing ultra-premium expressions like 'The Thirty,' directly targets these high-margin segments.\n\nWhile specific financial data for Glenmorangie alone (e.g., revenue, profit margins, cost of goods sold, marketing spend as a percentage of revenue) is not publicly disclosed by LVMH [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEfQtin6xo-CKHVhollqwPdEOTfku9LwBbHC6a5PF7uyo3or68MkyZ_BBYKzEZT5NpjPYzoDnQaZGfa_0ZZ0wxjUHePU2RNeZgDJmED3M2v6UlF-GcliwWj_dquuEdlpeCz2nBY3EWUthTPvtS7PG_jO8HfL4Z9-Ff5drW0GvvGk76T1diKvrQ74KI=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHY7ZUcFuFu7ejQwDDy_JS61-ouluvtS0_1PXIR76rx0MPyB0wQV5LCRLYtmwUI7K4e5UYJ_96qDL5b53JcVnP0-57-4vH8NJTec2hYt6B1oy2vl74aNk7hk0ADJi9wkfVIN-3XLOn7wx8LLCUc25WcSQPJOoZpVCqwBrnwLwZFD0wxDbwAY2g8XTm45Z_8XMzQhBqjTdCHv24o4tVtgyBDHv0JMy_pGM_sB91v9VoxaXb_HOJ-38H-YfO-MA==], we can infer its financial health from The Glenmorangie Company's performance (which includes Ardbeg). The Glenmorangie Company reported a significant surge in pre-tax profit, nearly **60% increase to £46.9 million in 2022**, up from £29.5 million in 2021 [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHY7ZUcFuFu7ejQwDDy_JS61-ouluvtS0_1PXIR76rx0MPyB0wQV5LCRLYtmwUI7K4e5UYJ_96qDL5b53JcVnP0-57-4vH8NJTec2hYt6B1oy2vl74aNk7hk0ADJi9wkfVIN-3XLOn7wx8LLCUc25WcSQPJOoZpVCqwBrnwLwZFD0wxDbwAY2g8XTm45Z_8XMzQhBqjTdCHv24o4tVtgyBDHv0JMy_pGM_sB91v9VoxaXb_HOJ-38H-YfO-MA==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGXAlyn1NKkgkWliAjZ9s42CyAZv7l6AjSqp-ra0hKsOKu-N4O1yFVEu4QZDFp0eZQk0n7as0dW6xykAJLb3pJTt0Eh8GeiMN6DfvdjNx7GyPnILax5vhJg0DuCNd005jKu_wMNn6WMUhcW2Z0dqyZmYeTbu7HAJ-vLh_-BRhNLp8JzG9AP68H0LcYB]. Turnover also increased substantially by **47% to £148.7 million in 2022** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHY7ZUcFuFu7ejQwDDy_JS61-ouluvtS0_1PXIR76rx0MPyB0wQV5LCRLYtmwUI7K4e5UYJ_96qDL5b53JcVnP0-57-4vH8NJTec2hYt6B1oy2vl74aNk7hk0ADJi9wkfVIN-3XLOn7wx8LLCUc25WcSQPJOoZpVCqwBrnwLwZFD0wxDbwAY2g8XTm45Z_8XMzQhBqjTdCHv24o4tVtgyBDHv0JMy_pGM_sB91v9VoxaXb_HOJ-38H-YfO-MA==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGXAlyn1NKkgkWliAjZ9s42CyAZv7l6AjSqp-ra0hKsOKu-N4O1yFVEu4QZDFp0eZQk0n7as0dW6xykAJLb3pJTt0Eh8GeiMN6DfvdjNx7GyPnILax5vhJg0DuCNd005jKu_wMNn6WMUhcW2Z0dqyZmYeTbu7HAJ-vLh_-BRhNLp8JzG9AP68H0LcYB]. This growth was primarily driven by strong export performance, with exports increasing by **45% to £128.4 million in 2022**, particularly in key markets such as the US, Germany, India, and South Korea [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHY7ZUcFuFu7ejQwDDy_JS61-ouluvtS0_1PXIR76rx0MPyB0wQV5LCRLYtmwUI7K4e5UYJ_96qDL5b53JcVnP0-57-4vH8NJTec2hYt6B1oy2vl74aNk7hk0ADJi9wkfVIN-3XLOn7wx8LLCUc25WcSQPJOoZpVCqwBrnwLwZFD0wxDbwAY2g8XTm45Z_8XMzQhBqjTdCHv24o4tVtgyBDHv0JMy_pGM_sB91v9VoxaXb_HOJ-38H-YfO-MA==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGXAlyn1NKkgkWliAjZ9s42CyAZv7l6AjSqp-ra0hKsOKu-N4O1yFVEu4QZDFp0eZQk0n7as0dW6xykAJLb3pJTt0Eh8GeiMN6DfvdjNx7GyPnILax5vhJg0DuCNd005jKu_wMNn6WMUhcW2Z0dqyZmYeTbu7HAJ-vLh_-BRhNLp8JzG9AP68H0LcYB].\n\nHowever, the broader LVMH Wines & Spirits division experienced a slowdown and decline in organic revenue and profit from recurring operations from 2023 to 2025. Organic revenue declined by **8% in 2024** and a further **5% in 2025**, with profit from recurring operations falling by **36% in 2024 to €1.356 billion** and an additional **25% in 2025 to €1.02 billion** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEyWZw-DDLd5-odmtZMzahgYpE1HEg3V8UtSI8yoTWJo-tFBvlctG1L0x46YjaG9XlCkzlx7nkkadoJ0e7YvIR6zj0QYTaOZ1M5tBzUZm9LTxglSNfLcbfl4R2lVV1VaTiMvxY6xXbuZWyOEmeZiFL_rX4DrQH2Xp8Y27jTMD9ev8MAvYrbTnz-S9U4zA==\", https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHHFH45bsmyi6_90i5VZynVV6iYm_m7JJ7UCTeZjDrn-WJoIMnA7VSmH0E2-PyCDnjG5pweX5ODiDlKtugVF3ecnMOYEzz-yp7_iVbcUnMVXb6gK0oRFvVUnVCiUScJWmsb3iEyowlIjLty38ubl94t0dBM4wkeeV7DhUKOhDMVCOIvVDGwcxoIC-DyR4G-Ttg==\"]. This downturn was primarily attributed to the post-COVID normalization of demand for Cognac and Champagne, trade tensions, and inventory adjustments in key markets like China and the United States [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEfQtin6xo-CKHVhollqwPdEOTfku9LwBbHC6a5PF7uyo3or68MkyZ_BBYKzEZT5NpjPYzoDnQaZGfa_0ZZ0wxjUHePU2RNeZgDJmED3M2v6UlF-GcliwWj_dquuEdlpeCz2nBY3EWUthTPvtS7PG_jO8HfL4Z9-Ff5drW0GvvGk76T1diKvrQ74KI=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEyWZw-DDLd5-odmtZMzahgYpE1HEg3V8UtSI8yoTWJo-tFBvlctG1L0x46YjaG9XlCkzlx7nkkadoJ0e7YvIR6zj0QYTaOZ1M5tBzUZm9LTxglSNfLcbfl4R2lVV1VaTiMvxY6xXbuZWyOEmeZiFL_rX4DrQH2Xp8Y27jTMD9ev8MAvYrbTnz-S9U4zA==\"].\n\nThe US market, while remaining Scotch whisky's largest by value at **$1.23 billion in 2024**, experienced a decline in premium single malt sales (down **17.2% in 2024**) and overall Scotch sales (fell **6% in the first nine months of 2025**) [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEfQtin6xo-CKHVhollqwPdEOTfku9LwBbHC6a5PF7uyo3or68MkyZ_BBYKzEZT5NpjPYzoDnQaZGfa_0ZZ0wxjUHePU2RNeZgDJmED3M2v6UlF-GcliwWj_dquuEdlpeCz2nBY3EWUthTPvtS7PG_jO8HfL4Z9-Ff5drW0GvvGk76T1diKvrQ74KI=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHHFH45bsmyi6_90i5VZynVV6iYm_m7JJ7UCTeZjDrn-WJoIMnA7VSmH0E2-PyCDnjG5pweX5ODiDlKtugVF3ecnMOYEzz-yp7_iVbcUnMVXb6gK0oRFvVUnVCiUScJWmsb3iEyowlIjLty38ubl94t0dBM4wkeeV7DhUKOhDMVCOIvVDGwcxoIC-DyR4G-Ttg==\"]. This decline was influenced by global cost-of-living pressures and a **10% tariff on Scotch whisky imports in 2025** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEfQtin6xo-CKHVhollqwPdEOTfku9LwBbHC6a5PF7uyo3or68MkyZ_BBYKzEZT5NpjPYzoDnQaZGfa_0ZZ0wxjUHePU2RNeZgDJmED3M2v6UlF-GcliwWj_dquuEdlpeCz2nBY3EWUthTPvtS7PG_jO8HfL4Z9-Ff5drW0GvvGk76T1diKvrQ74KI=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHHFH45bsmyi6_90i5VZynVV6iYm_m7JJ7UCTeZjDrn-WJoIMnA7VSmH0E2-PyCDnjG5pweX5ODiDlKtugVF3ecnMOYEzz-yp7_iVbcUnMVXb6gK0oRFvVUnVCiUScJWmsb3iEyowlIjLty38ubl94t0dBM4wkeeV7DhUKOhDMVCOIvVDGwcxoIC-DyR4G-Ttg==\"].\n\n"},{"level":3,"title":"White-Space Opportunities:","content":"\n1.  **Ready-To-Drink (RTD) and No/Low Alcohol Expressions:**\n    *   **Market Size & Growth:** The global RTD cocktails market was valued at **USD 3.76 billion in 2025** and is projected to reach **USD 13.86 billion by 2034**, exhibiting a CAGR of **15.59% from 2026 to 2034** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF1kkHNdOzWDxw49sL537qKp3EyV-nYZid0jrcd07lnnH8kvRBho89nm1D6RrxyQghp4YQ-6EKpu02L-Rbt3GMRzSIcAm_d2R3x-Lm3ZyxA5GlF31FI7703UCTps1odbKz5Zv_-pkPxuQvWBTklFlqYRD0Xk-h3SOkUNxbye70=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGmG4ce4RsrYVL3uPGegKDZSLpUx401yhi08czBbIOreZaauLhdje70WM-HxivFeWHW6nff2ut8yr4cPcV8KXzMc5De4b7tAmyR16uEtkplXFoGoNMTjmDeDd6gIy1Wq3nWFRI64vZH9aKeV7_sDFdOQTfG11Yq8xv6iZh42clzQWk7RIyX_tMRASw6c5lYsHeOf_7ml9N0]. The broader RTD alcoholic beverages market is projected to grow from **US$25.8 billion in 2026 to US$42.4 billion by 2033**, at a CAGR of **6.3%** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGgXZzIRNIfdcmd0tr11e3GeyCZPJjA6Euu6yb3iapVBtLWZrp_4qZsuRPypVU8sz-8S61SfBfwWmj5Eg9VPO59A2YOvVJ-WgEaQc5Az1A65g8i-QUROniuSmeWtbMoaFSSEiZKvyosFbAhVYprBuixUk4dobbIbdLhdv1zSQ4JU7NUoyIPk7jHGLmpisrGc1iUKdA=].\n    *   The global no- and low-alcohol market was valued at nearly **USD 20 billion in 2023**, doubling from 2019, and is expected to deliver incremental growth of **USD 4 billion by 2028** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHKBC48uLo1u5glO4iVmJ9xStVcuxjZAbif1m_OfxuBAKeWSTOGkGvcjLJMDujk_69znc9h-nOwk34biHfUwFcPGJ2Y_V35FCLudfXdZIG8t5ILixXwFJc0n_m65pgVA8gs8eHSDXroFH7fiy9swIAhzr89r_mB8A5Pgpy9Xm-bGcgJFM9tIGSlxYTRZpjws3mTdJD5O6cKnU5b33lLi8UaC9ukO4JjuQfIokyRNwyW050sexq0PYmXcZdELrfZCTFJm-_TZiRpX5lCoornpM3y35XNW-rh67QExPWpkNCLqDMyqvPsAwTPL4kEPT_smA==\", https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGgXZzIRNIfdcmd0tr11e3GeyCZPJjA6Euu6yb3iapVBtLWZrp_4qZsuRPypVU8sz-8S61SfBfwWmj5Eg9VPO59A2YOvVJ-WgEaQc5Az1A65g8i-QUROniuSmeWtbMoaFSSEiZKvyosFbAhVYprBuixUk4dobbIbdLhdv1zSQ4JU7NUoyIPk7jHGLmpisrGc1iUKdA=]. The no-alcohol segment is projected to grow at a **7% volume CAGR between 2024 and 2028**, while the combined no/low-alcohol market is expected to expand by a **4% volume CAGR through 2028** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGgXZzIRNIfdcmd0tr11e3GeyCZPJjA6Euu6yb3iapVBtLWZrp_4qZsuRPypVU8sz-8S61SfBfwWmj5Eg9VPO59A2YOvVJ-WgEaQc5Az1A65g8i-QUROniuSmeWtbMoaFSSEiZKvyosFbAhVYprBuixUk4dobbIbdLhdv1zSQ4JU7NUoyIPk7jHGLmpisrGc1iUKdA=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH-Dk3DYoSoFO_wT7g-xDwX3XZWaedoG3hpuTZYWWbqmj4oxRsIMgsDWAZsPJ7M0p1lDEqh-wzkKk2Eccd1ky1yh01RpDkHpYC3NZBhG7kopbBXksq3Nk-5jy9M_bOgRljmBAkA-Qc-fBjxSS8NNoKQ8NFuYm0sDGo0oADYvxzG1hQEa6JAVy5UoL3C_mfS1xi4RPr7sVNQGx9UQl-v7VnVmpDVvYy9whtPJ84I3mU=].\n    *   **Target Demographics:** Millennials and Gen Z are key drivers for both RTD and no/low alcohol categories, with **57% of US RTD consumers being Millennials or Gen Zs** and **43% of US no/low consumers being Millennials** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEDIbEJZNoN1QK2mOLDeI4wmPaXfLj74RrL8Ah7wE5Vt_Ebyd_2ZwfL03d2OzT837M4jf1ibCwX5IzlPCFvnPX5G29sYpfEo3BZoWKPPm3vIOjplQuJ87atjm0iHzL7mEv84_C84FWzX2L-1A_d2kDgoD7K8ZZzJfpAYEYOMNXoB6FaXanAPPmF, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGgXZzIRNIfdcmd0tr11e3GeyCZPJjA6Euu6yb3iapVBtLWZrp_4qZsuRPypVU8sz-8S61SfBfwWmj5Eg9VPO59A2YOvVJ-WgEaQc5Az1A65g8i-QUROniuSmeWtbMoaFSSEiZKvyosFbAhVYprBuixUk4dobbIbdLhdv1zSQ4JU7NUoyIPk7jHGLmpisrGc1iUKdA=]. These consumers prioritize convenience, health-conscious options, and novel flavor experiences.\n    *   **Geographic Focus:** North America holds the largest share in the RTD alcoholic beverages market (**41% of total volume in 2026**) and the RTD spirits market [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGgXZzIRNIfdcmd0tr11e3GeyCZPJjA6Euu6yb3iapVBtLWZrp_4qZsuRPypVU8sz-8S61SfBfwWmj5Eg9VPO59A2YOvVJ-WgEaQc5Az1A65g8i-QUROniuSmeWtbMoaFSSEiZKvyosFbAhVYprBuixUk4dobbIbdLhdv1zSQ4JU7NUoyIPk7jHGLmpisrGc1iUKdA=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHKBC48uLo1u5glO4iVmJ9xStVcuxjZAbif1m_OfxuBAKeWSTOGkGvcjLJMDujk_69znc9h-nOwk34biHfUwFcPGJ2Y_V35FCLudfXdZIG8t5ILixXwFJc0n_m65pgVA8gs8eHSDXroFH7fiy9swIAhzr89r_mB8A5Pgpy9Xm-bGcgJFM9tIGSlxYTRZpjws3mTdJD5O6cKnU5b33lLi8UaC9ukO4JjuQfIokyRNwyW050sexq0PYmXcZdELrfZCTFJm-_TZiRpX5lCoornpM3y35XNW-rh67QExPWpkNCLqDMyqvPsAwTPL4kEPT_smA==\"]. Asia Pacific is the fastest-growing region for RTD alcoholic beverages and has the highest growth potential for overall RTD beverages [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGgXZzIRNIfdcmd0tr11e3GeyCZPJjA6Euu6yb3iapVBtLWZrp_4qZsuRPypVU8sz-8S61SfBfwWmj5Eg9VPO59A2YOvVJ-WgEaQc5Az1A65g8i-QUROniuSmeWtbMoaFSSEiZKvyosFbAhVYprBuixUk4dobbIbdLhdv1zSQ4JU7NUoyIPk7jHGLmpisrGc1iUKdA=]. Europe is the largest market for low-alcohol beverages [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGgXZzIRNIfdcmd0tr11e3GeyCZPJjA6Euu6yb3iapVBtLWZrp_4qZsuRPypVU8sz-8S61SfBfwWmj5Eg9VPO59A2YOvVJ-WgEaQc5Az1A65g8i-QUROniuSmeWtbMoaFSSEiZKvyosFbAhVYprBuixUk4dobbIbdLhdv1zSQ4JU7NUoyIPk7jHGLmpisrGc1iUKdA=].\n    *   **Glenmorangie's Current Position:** Glenmorangie's 'X by Glenmorangie,' launched in April 2021, is a single malt specifically designed for mixing in cocktails, demonstrating a step towards approachability and targeting younger consumers [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGgXZzIRNIfdcmd0tr11e3GeyCZPJjA6Euu6yb3iapVBtLWZrp_4qZsuRPypVU8sz-8S61SfBfwWmj5Eg9VPO59A2YOvVJ-WgEaQc5Az1A65g8i-QUROniuSmeWtbMoaFSSEiZKvyosFbAhVYprBuixUk4dobbIbdLhdv1zSQ4JU7NUoyIPk7jHGLmpisrGc1iUKdA=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEDIbEJZNoN1QK2mOLDeI4wmPaXfLj74RrL8Ah7wE5Vt_Ebyd_2ZwfL03d2OzT837M4jf1ibCwX5IzlPCFvnPX5G29sYpfEo3BZoWKPPm3vIOjplQuJ87atjm0iHzL7mEv84_C84FWzX2L-1A_d2kDgoD7K8ZZzJfpAYEYOMNXoB6FaXanAPPmF]. However, the brand has not yet entered the pre-packaged RTD or dedicated no/low alcohol segments, representing a significant missed opportunity to capture these growing markets. The global alcohol-free spirit market was valued at **USD 1.52 billion in 2025** and is expected to reach **USD 5.85 billion by 2035**, growing at a CAGR of **14.43% from 2026-2035** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGI-SovfXXUCwb6aQ6iV8PmZ5mqf0DG_1No2D7pZZER4N1pe9GxtPQBn_DgJvPsMKhNxrDgIzkjO1yKB33J1CnwteSOPHENZ8GIEelEvdbpt4ngOt2k42M0Pph6FkBCrzHmwZVAo0w_t31LO2qslmM774veh_Qy-fKoOQWURQl-tO5TJ4ssjbiA_eh7]. The US no-alcohol spirits segment is the fastest-growing in the spirits category, with a **5-year CAGR exceeding 60% through 2024** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGRzaG6po7DeSu1dJV85_7eOm90m2K5FaKCpDC01w6-aU8CW2XELZUdez2r9vgmtKXuqDgzYjL4retqQW0APMYHf_7j4E4zoq_8U4k2aXOP18YrCPzKQA2D_APf3SuB7oZQaLYK96AHaozSXi4EbsgZSi1U5X6GInCtVafZpouBUaO5AXLe3Y=]. The global RTD spirits market was valued at **USD 5.74 billion in 2025** and is projected to grow to **USD 7.67 billion by 2032** at a CAGR of **4.2%** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGI-SovfXXUCwb6aQ6iV8PmZ5mqf0DG_1No2D7pZZER4N1pe9GxtPQBn_DgJvPsMKhNxrDgIzkjO1yKB33J1CnwteSOPHENZ8GIEelEvdbpt4ngOt2k42M0Pph6FkBCrzHmwZVAo0w_t31LO2qslmM774veh_Qy-fKoOQWURQl-tO5TJ4ssjbiA_eh7]. Another projection indicates a CAGR of **10.2% for RTDs from 2021-2025 (volume)** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGgXZzIRNIfdcmd0tr11e3GeyCZPJjA6Euu6yb3iapVBtLWZrp_4qZsuRPypVU8sz-8S61SfBfwWmj5Eg9VPO59A2YOvVJ-WgEaQc5Az1A65g8i-QUROniuSmeWtbMoaFSSEiZKvyosFbAhVYprBuixUk4dobbIbdLhdv1zSQ4JU7NUoyIPk7jHGLmpisrGc1iUKdA=].\n\n---\n\n"},{"level":2,"title":"STRATEGIC SYNTHESIS — SO WHAT FOR LIQUID & THE BRAND","content":"\nGlenmorangie, under LVMH, is clearly executing a robust premiumization strategy, increasing age statements and introducing ultra-premium expressions. While this drives value, recent U.S. volume declines and broader LVMH Wines & Spirits revenue drops indicate challenges in maintaining growth across all segments. This presents significant opportunities for Liquid.\n\n"},{"level":3,"title":"What's Left on the Table for Glenmorangie:","content":"\n1.  **Under-exploited \"Approachability\" & \"Occasion-based\" Marketing:** While Glenmorangie aims for approachability and targets younger consumers for cocktails (e.g., 'X by Glenmorangie'), the core brand messaging, even with Harrison Ford, still leans into traditional Scotch narratives. The 40% ABV for 'The Original' further supports approachability, but this isn't explicitly leveraged for new consumption occasions beyond cocktails. There's a gap in translating \"delicious and wonderful\" into diverse, everyday premium moments that resonate with the broader, younger, and female audience they seek.\n\n    **Improved Resolution for \"Approachability\" & \"Occasion-based\" Marketing:** Glenmorangie's existing 'Delicious and Wonderful' campaign, launched in 2020, is a strong foundation for attracting younger consumers and women by promoting inclusivity and approachability [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGni8WROhiORP1OOj1b_C2E49B6IrpX-ElzJIWmY8ODG9Bmb1poxNL8P_gIJigCVJ4bPLRa2rZV8gxQg69TMoPXiRP4z6CpaGjV_uqGPOMSUledUg2yYiZUWDdhcUh693lpZppdGOrJAOTPMjLABjITs1Q9s2iLs3vpCaZyhSM3U1B5wg==]. However, to move beyond general messaging and effectively activate these white-space demographics, Glenmorangie needs to implement specific, data-driven strategies. This includes targeted product innovation with unique cask finishes, developing and widely sharing cocktail-centric content, authentic partnerships with diverse influencers, and a robust e-commerce and experiential marketing presence. Capitalizing on the rapid growth of alcohol e-commerce (projected to reach $161.4 billion by 2030 with a 16.9% CAGR [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGni8WROhiORP1OOj1b_C2E49B6IrpX-ElzJIWmY8ODG9Bmb1poxNL8P_gIJigCVJ4bPLRa2rZV8gxQg69TMoPXiRP4z6CpaGjV_uqGPOMSUledUg2yYiZUWDdhcUh693lpZppdGOrJAOTPMjLABjITs1Q9s2iLs3vpCaZyhSM3U1B5wg==]) and the gifting culture in travel retail (63% of spirits purchased as gifts [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGni8WROhiORP1OOj1b_C2E49B6IrpX-ElzJIWmY8ODG9Bmb1poxNL8P_gIJigCVJ4bPLRa2rZV8gxQg69TMoPXiRP4z6CpaGjV_uqGPOMSUledUg2yYiZUWDdhcUh693lpZppdGOrJAOTPMjLABjITs1Q9s2iLs3vpCaZyhSM3U1B5wg==]) through tailored offerings and distribution strategies will be crucial. The global Scotch whisky market was valued at **USD 56.51 billion in 2025** and is projected to grow to **USD 73.63 billion by 2031**, demonstrating a Compound Annual Growth Rate (CAGR) of **4.61%** [https://www.mordorintelligence.com/industry-reports/scotch-whisky-market, https://www.techsciresearch.com/report/scotch-whisky-market/20496.html]. Other estimates place the 2025 Scotch whisky market size at **USD 34.89 billion**, with a projected growth to **USD 52.16 billion by 2031** at a **6.93% CAGR** [https://market.us/report/scotch-whisky-market/, https://www.precedenceresearch.com/scotch-whisky-market]. The single malt Scotch whisky segment is projected to expand at a CAGR of **8.34% from USD 10.42 billion in 2025 to USD 19.55 billion by 2034** [https://www.fortunebusinessinsights.com/single-malt-scotch-whisky-market-108208, https://trendxinsights.com/report/scotch-whisky-market].\n\n    **Recommendations for \"Approachability\" & \"Occasion-based\" Marketing:**\n    *   **Targeted Product Innovation for New Occasions:** Develop and market specific expressions or limited editions designed for particular occasions or flavor profiles that appeal to younger consumers and women. This could include lighter, fruitier whiskies or those with unique cask finishes (e.g., 'A Tale of Ice Cream,' 'A Tale of Spices' [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHF-n57G-dPjLph3l7JZR58k0u-YfgB1LfQDc7MZ8kLfMCGRlzga-pR2IkojoePnzFIlMQi8S6FVuuQX123BDKJVnNDvemQh2DLfwARSXdrXNdK4uXfkZpOS-OmQV47DAFNPQ5ARWxgmtMILHInYDMzzDiU1SCb8-MUbMtRcJDdjJMYUYgdUZF4jVc,\n"}]
